snippet.title: Murky Divers - Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Get a peek at the trouble you'll find in Murky Divers, an upcoming co-op comedy horror game coming to Steam on June 19, 2024.

Murky Divers is a co-op comedy horror where Lethal Company meets Subnautica as you and your team work together to explore dangerous abandoned wrecks and destroy evidence of the shady experiments your lab has been undertaking.

#Gaming #Games #IGN
